            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么不建议自己掏耳朵#</span></a> 一不小心可能引起感染😱😱】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#掏耳朵有哪些注意事项#</span></a>？医生表示，原则上不建议掏耳朵，自行掏耳朵要注意：①器具干净，不能张三掏了李四掏。②掏的深度一定要掌握好，太深了有可能导致鼓膜穿孔。③力度要适中，在自己感觉到没有耳痛的前提下掏耳朵相对更安全。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%8D%E7%9B%B2%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%8D%E7%9B%B2%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不要再盲掏耳朵了#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6NP1CFm" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
