            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[生病]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shengbing-b740fa9852.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B2%89%E6%B5%B8%E5%BC%8F%E5%80%92%E6%98%A5%E5%AF%92%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%86%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B2%89%E6%B5%B8%E5%BC%8F%E5%80%92%E6%98%A5%E5%AF%92%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%86%E6%9D%A5%E8%A2%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#沉浸式倒春寒即将来袭#</span></a>，收好这份养生指南】最近，北方多地气温暖如初夏。不过今天起，一股全能型冷空气将影响我国大部地区，北方将沉浸式体验“倒春寒”，南方也将重启“湿凉模式”。天气忽冷忽热，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%80%92%E6%98%A5%E5%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%80%92%E6%98%A5%E5%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些人群要注意倒春寒#</span></a>？气温跳水，“春捂”重点“捂”哪里？9图了解👇🏻（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj2093h63j20rs0vdtjo.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj209juabj20rs0vd48v.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj209z0npj20rs0vd4a5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj208k4ctj20rs0vdtjj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj20adx4qj20rs0oxdok.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj20arw58j20rs0vdal8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj20b4h7fj20rs0vdtk3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcj20bi74aj20rs0vdqdm.jpg" referrerpolicy